Package ClientInterfaces Description

This package encompasses all classes required for successful interfacing of operations to be used by the user.

This includes providing an interface for connecting to the SKLM server, interface between the user and the library, and POJO classes describing properties of the connection (Connection) and the key properties requested by the user (KeyUniqueIDMap).

Since:
1.0
